SMS Number Types in Service Cloud

Select the ideal type of phone number for providing customer service over text. Whether you choose a short code, long code, or both depends on your business needs.

Available in: Lightning Experience.

This article applies to: Standard and enhanced SMS channels.
This article doesn’t apply to: Messaging for In-App, Messaging for Web, standard and enhanced WhatsApp, standard and enhanced Facebook Messenger, enhanced Apple Messages for Business, and Bring Your Own Channel.

IMPORTANT Standard SMS channels are scheduled for retirement. Upgrade your standard SMS channels to enhanced channels before February 14, 2026.

For number availability by country basis, see Messaging Regulations by Country. Salesforce will text-enable numbers on behalf of its customers.

The following table details the number type available for the most common use cases:
